item.title: Lil' chestnut
item.description: Here's an anectode: long time ago the Polish pope would borrow my grandma’s horse when visiting the mountains. That’s the only remaining picture of Kasztanek (lil’ chestnut) we have. Happy times.
item.content:encoded:
Lil' chestnut

Here's an anectode: long time ago the Polish pope would borrow my grandma’s horse when visiting the mountains. That’s the only remaining picture of Kasztanek (lil’ chestnut) we have. Happy times.
